<devicesets>
<deviceset name="WRIS-PSMC_2512" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:13351063/2" prefix="R" library_version="2">
<description>&lt;b&gt; WRIS-PSMC Metal Plate Resistors
&lt;br&gt;High Power Current Sensing
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Characteristics
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt; 
&lt;br&gt;Product series for high power current sensing up to 2 W Mounting style: SMT-Chip (standard terminal)
&lt;br&gt;Resistance range: 2 mΩ ‒ 10 mΩ
&lt;br&gt;Resistance tolerance: ±1%; ±5%
&lt;br&gt;Rated Power: 2 W
&lt;br&gt;TCR: ±100 ppm/°C
&lt;br&gt;Operating temperature: -55°C up to +155°C
&lt;br&gt;Size: 2512
&lt;br&gt;Recommended soldering: Reflow soldering

&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Ignition coil &amp; igniter
&lt;br&gt;Motor control
&lt;br&gt;Inverter
&lt;br&gt;Battery pack
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Package name and Variant abbreviation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;L X W X H X PW =Length X Width X Height X Pad Width
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://katalog.we-online.com/media/images/v2/o135744v209%20Family_WRIS-PSMC.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://katalog.we-online.com/media/images/v2/o135744v209%20Family_WRIS-PSMC.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="https://katalog.we-online.com/en/pbs/WRIS-PSMC"&gt;https://katalog.we-online.com/en/pbs/WRIS-PSMC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;Created by Ella Wu  2019-09-05&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;2019(C) Wurth Elektronik</description>
